cs.CR, cs.GT, cs.DC, cs.CY, cs.SI 

The paper deals with the design of a secure Blockchain network framework to prevent damages from an attacker. This involves the application of the strategic alliance of the management on top of the recent developed stochastic game framework. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the categories of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.CY (Computers and Society), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
